## Next build steps

1. Replace heuristics with tracked-object logic (YOLO + tracker) while preserving scoring/trigger contract.
2. Persist alerts/metrics in Postgres and artifacts in S3 (instead of local disk).
3. Add deduplication windows, suppression rules, and operator feedback loop.
4. Add auth, tenant routing, and signed webhook delivery.

